# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050


//Showing my name
### Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/



### Get all books
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books

### Get book by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1

### Search by author 
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?author=Alex

### Searching by title 
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?title=Node




### Full-text q (title or author)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?q=node

